’Ù@94b45b2961d00d61df711fe5380a9aaefc7c5444001e7fc91729035b73bb57b3Ú¹Title: title: bytes starts-with
Path: Examples
Content:
Checks if binary starts with 
``0x[1F FF AA]``
.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[1F FF AA AA] | bytes starts-with 0x[1F FF AA]
true

```
Checks if binary starts with 
``0x[1F]``
.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[1F FF AA AA] | bytes starts-with 0x[1F]
true

```
Checks if binary starts with 
``0x[1F]``
.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[1F FF AA AA] | bytes starts-with 0x[11]
false

```
